    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3712933/" class="title-link">另一种正面战场</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3712933"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/resurrection/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2308075-11.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/resurrection/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">姚澜</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-22"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-22 08:10:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3712933_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  说抗日不一定是为记住国恨家仇，而是为剖析自己曾经的错误和不堪，或者说，作为一段历史，抗日应该被记住，但很悲哀的是抗日被作为传播仇恨的工具而滥用……在今时今日，正面推广此书也是另一种正面战场。稍感可惜的是，限于审查，发行版比网络版少了不少“料”

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3712933/#comments">(3回应)</a>
